c?w=1600&amp;q=80"/><link rel="preload" as="image" href="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1571896349842-33c89424de2d?w=1600&amp;q=80"/><link rel="preload" as="image" href="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1520250497591-112f2f40a3f4?w=1600&amp;q=80"/><link rel="preload" as="image" href="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518733057094-95b53143d2a7?w=1600&amp;q=80"/><div hidden id="S:2"><div class="pt-32"><section class="px-6 pb-20"><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto"><span class="label-mono">Le Sanctuaire</span><h1 class="editorial-heading text-6xl md:text-8xl mt-6 mb-8">Designing the <span class="text-gradient-gold italic">future</span> of hospitality</h1><p class="text-xl font-serif text-ink-200 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed mb-6">Nous faisons évoluer le paysage des loisirs. Nos futurs projets sont un dialogue entre l&#x27;innovation architecturale et la beauté sauvage de l&#x27;Éthiopie. Des retraites de montagne de luxe aux sanctuaires nichés au cœur des forêts, nous concevons des espaces qui transcendent l&#x27;hébergement traditionnel, offrant un sens profond du lieu dans un monde de plus en plus éphémère.</p><p class="text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-gold-400">L&#x27;Avenir : Durable. Visionnaire. Éternel.</p></div></section><section class="px-6 py-24 border-t border-ink-800/50"><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto"><h2 class="editorial-heading text-4xl mb-12">Pipeline de projets</h2><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6"><a class="group block" href="/fr/sanctuary/wagela-forest-retreat"><div class="aspect-[4/3] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-ink-900 mb-4 relative"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542718610-a1d656d1884c?w=1600&amp;q=80" alt="Wagela Forest Retreat" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105"/><span class="absolute top-4 left-4 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-gold-500 text-ink-900 text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-widest">design</span></div><p class="label-mono text-ink-400 mb-1">Wagela Highlands, Oromia</p><h3 class="font-serif text-2xl group-hover:text-gold-400 transition-colors">Wagela Forest Retreat</h3></a><a class="group block" href="/fr/sanctuary/rift-valley-lakehouse"><div class="aspect-[4/3] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-ink-900 mb-4 relative"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1571896349842-33c89424de2d?w=1600&amp;q=80" alt="Rift Valley Lakehouse" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105"/><span class="absolute top-4 left-4 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-gold-500 text-ink-900 text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-widest">planning</span></div><p class="label-mono text-ink-400 mb-1">Rift Valley Lakes Region</p><h3 class="font-serif text-2xl group-hover:text-gold-400 transition-colors">Rift Valley Lakehouse</h3></a><a class="group block" href="/fr/sanctuary/bale-mountain-lodge"><div class="aspect-[4/3] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-ink-900 mb-4 relative"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1520250497591-112f2f40a3f4?w=1600&amp;q=80" alt="Bale Mountain Lodge" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105"/><span class="absolute top-4 left-4 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-gold-500 text-ink-900 text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-widest">construction</span></div><p class="label-mono text-ink-400 mb-1">Bale Mountains National Park</p><h3 class="font-serif text-2xl group-hover:text-gold-400 transition-colors">Bale Mountain Lodge</h3></a><a class="group block" href="/fr/sanctuary/simien-cliffside-spa"><div class="aspect-[4/3] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-ink-900 mb-4 relative"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518733057094-95b53143d2a7?w=1600&amp;q=80" alt="Simien Cliffside Spa" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105"/><span class="absolute top-4 left-4 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-gold-500 text-ink-900 text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-widest">design</span></div><p class="label-mono text-ink-400 mb-1">Simien Mountains, Amhara</p><h3 class="font-serif text-2xl group-hover:text-gold-400 transition-colors">Simien Cliffside Spa</h3></a></div></div></section><section class="px-6 py-32 border-t border-ink-800/50 bg-ink-900/30"><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16"><div><span class="label-mono">Philosophie de design</span><h2 class="editorial-heading text-4xl mt-4 mb-6">Sustainable luxury</h2><p class="text-lg text-ink-200 leading-relaxed">Éthos de luxe durable.</p></div><div><span class="label-mono">Thèse d&#x27;investissement</span><h2 class="editorial-heading text-4xl mt-4 mb-6">Once-in-a-generation</h2><p class="text-lg text-ink-200 leading-relaxed">Une fenêtre unique pour l&#x27;investissement hôtelier visionnaire.</p></div></div></section><section class="px-6 py-32 border-t border-ink-800/50"><div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center"><span class="label-mono">Commandes sur mesure</span><h2 class="editorial-heading text-5xl mt-4 mb-6">Have land? Have a vision?</h2><p class="text-xl text-ink-200 font-serif mb-8">Vous avez un terrain ? Nous construisons.</p><a class="btn-primary text-lg" href="/fr/contact">Start a Conversation</a></div></section></div></div><script>$RS=function(a,b){a=document.getElementById(a);b=document.getElementById(b);for(a.parentNode.removeChild(a);a.firstChild;)b.parentNode.insertBefore(a.firstChild,b);b.parentNode.removeChild(b)};$RS("S:2","P:2")</script><script>$RC("B:1","S:1")</script></body></html>